quoteText: we may change the software or other data in the SIM card remotely and without notice, and we may utilize any capacity in the SIM card for administrative, network, business and/or commercial purposes.
title: Visbible can change the software on your SIM card at anytime without notice.

tosdr.tldr: Visible can change the software on your sim card at any time and without any notice. This can be a security issue and  both, the Service and hackers, can install unwanted software like spyware or viruses.
